criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Patients receiving surgery under general anesthesia during 2018 in Peking Union
             Medical College Hospital and other medical centers participating in this study.

          -  Aged 18-70 years.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Previous surgery history;

          -  Preoperative chronic pain history;

          -  Injury;

          -  Have no access to mobile phone or website;

          -  Postoperative chronic infection;

          -  Non-radical incision of tumor or malignancy recurrence during follow-up;
